content:
Open Enrollment Periods
Fall Open Enrollment for all new fall semester students is July 1 - August 22, 2025.
Students must either enroll in the CMU medical SHIP or apply to waive it during this time.Â  The SHIP coverage period is August 1, 2025 - July 31, 2026.
